TITLE: Episode 18 - Amazon Strikes Back
DESCRIPTION: In this episode, Thaddeus and Gary discuss Disney+, the antitrust probe into Google, FCC Chairman Ajit Pai's appearance on The Rubin Report, and Amazon's response to losing that ten billion dollar Pentagon contract.
